The 24-inch necklace is great when worn alone or layered with a shorter length necklace (18-20").

14k gold fill is made by mixing solid gold with other alloy metals.  It wears like solid gold because its outer surface is solid gold.  The gold does not chip or flake off.  Gold filled jewelry will last for many years of wear when taken cared of properly and is a fantastic and affordable alternative to solid gold.
